data.description: Welcome to the hub of the Northern Neck- Kilmarnock Virginia! Nestled in the walkable neighborhoods is the newly renovated home built in 1940. New spacious bathroom with walk-in shower and updated vanity. All brand new flooring and appliances. New paint throughout. Fenced in yard for your pets! Walk to shopping, dining and more. Public water and sewer supply. High speed internet available. Handicap accessible features.
